nodes.text: Table 746b was a table in Frander's Bay where Lando Calrissian and Han Solo first encountered Taka Jamoreesa, whilst searching for a ship that would not be affiliated with the New Republic. At first Taka tried to impersonate Han but quickly figured out what the two were searching for. Taka claimed that they were looking for a ZV-9, since they came to Table 746b.
